{"tid":2491778,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":" ［超多圖］回歸前港英時代殖民政府餐具分享","createTime":"2021-04-16T14:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T14:52:50.000Z","uid":18063,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e927eacb3f5b16e7d47d265e0f4319fc14acfb4","tid":2491778,"uid":18063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSTBSbwPtsBeodW1pFVniH3q7xExQMUsBSBGpRTp7wVvu?filename=svEmUQR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsvEmUQR.jpg&h=c7367642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdqZhyzP2MmCp6CnPS6D1Ea1fjTC3FU1ncA56cqRW2xNK?filename=LSe2Ehw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSe2Ehw.jpg&h=73f817af&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n英殖香港嘅時候，呢種綠邊白瓷嘅餐具係流通於各個政府部門<br />\n政府辦公室、醫院、監獄等等嘅政府地方，都係用佢地<br />\n小弟覺得呢種咁靚，又咁有香港歷史價值嘅餐具，從以前嗰幾代個個都識，到到而家差不多被遺忘了，又無人為佢地記載，實在可惜<br />\n所以想喺度分享一下收藏，同埋我所知嘅歷史<br />\n而我其實自己在97年前都只係個小朋友，未曾有幸喺職場用過呢啲餐具<br />\n所以如果各位有任何補充，或者你都有收藏嘅話，非常歡迎大家嘅分享同討論！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRrVzJmLENDVSsh34BpS5gjVpn3Eqpr2dSKBy3tVgWzat?filename=D8XvOeH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8XvOeH.jpg&h=ff0c07ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n略略咁總括一下，以我所知，90年代前的餐具都是有HK皇冠（圖右）<br />\n而喺接近回歸嘅90年代，就變成只有HK沒有皇冠（圖中）<br />\n最後臨近回歸就只有空白（圖左）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcCru1cXw2VjnnYf9dZ23mkaNKt7wxxe4cgAw2Ed1tNuZ?filename=ZKyiW88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKyiW88.jpg&h=f0b52f3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而講到造瓷廠，喺最早期，大約50年代前的瓷器，係由英國出產<br />\n（圖中）就係DUNN BENNETT &amp; CO的英國製瓷碟<br />\n由於DUNN BENNETT製嘅瓷器年代相當久遠，所以現在是相當稀少<br />\n後來就由英國製轉為日本製<br />\n50年代開始就用（圖右）的日本製MATSUMURA &amp; CO<br />\n到到近代，就轉晒做日本的TOYO（圖左）<br />\n可以睇得出，唔同廠商製造嘅綠色同白色都有些微分別<br />\nTOYO嘅白色帶點灰啞，DUNN BENNETT嘅綠色又帶點青翠<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTL797qThBJN5PS5iD8iDEhUGbc7dvrhGMDpEBVrncS1H?filename=r2ux1Dk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2ux1Dk.jpg&h=485cd9e6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nTOYO出產的豉油碟（圖左）比較大隻，而且偏灰<br />\n而MATSUMURA出產的同樣係豉油碟（圖右），但就更細隻，而且偏白<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTHRKVCaVnGCd3d9pyD4aynjAg3FeJaJrV3N3gnkbB6ez?filename=y5jVeZ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5jVeZ9.jpg&h=138f7965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瓷器以茶具居多<br />\n上圖就係最為常見嘅兩款杯<br />\n圖左是咖啡杯，圖右是奶茶杯<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmacFY61K2spZh2PZ8xpoekeF2MHcadQsipQzLaFaheBMC?filename=Tx1DXd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTx1DXd5.jpg&h=049204bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n茶壺亦有大細之分<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme4RVfwzG9J2LB68XQ1ufa5BY9zUwzmvMgXPZxpPc9djH?filename=F1KujsC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1KujsC.jpg&h=50577fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而無論大茶壺或是細茶壺，都會有兩種款色<br />\n一款在壺嘴下會有三片綠葉（圖左），而另一款就無（圖右）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY4hjw1i38yFsVKqqDMLi7heFuHDSVoQxeUWhBmVijaoF?filename=aTKx1Gv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTKx1Gv.jpg&h=dfb238f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n奶壺亦有分大中細SIZE<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWYWPmGmHKp5M7baz7r3cUuXsaJ7bEhysxwgafS8UTABZ?filename=iTx7QBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiTx7QBc.jpg&h=65c7516c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瓷碟嘅SIZE就分得更多<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeLqwtCQw9cUoFn1Bb9bGkUCo9iyBu4xBZuNLxjBqFirN?filename=Y4qUvBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4qUvBc.jpg&h=f872c247&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n而呢種瓷器，有部分會出現「開片」嘅現象<br />\n開片即係瓷器嘅釉面隨住時間嘅洗禮，逐漸開裂嘅現象<br />\n裂開嘅其實只係釉彩，瓷嘅胎骨其實是無影響的，所以並不代表瓷器開裂<br />\n<br />\n以上就講左一啲籠統嘅資料，黎緊分享嘅就係一啲比較不確定嘅收藏"},{"pid":"14f3d7124799ac2f450b6b7995f496f9823d25ee","tid":2491778,"uid":1095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"1a353c9a11467545d0a10c64cde9c027f4a33b70","tid":2491778,"uid":16719,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmau4T5yFr1EEnKtT9CWkSRN4KKMz8jBwVqccc6VsgxeAo?filename=MSq9jyT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSq9jyT.png&h=cd41c4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係大清好"},{"pid":"2ace47b540eeb55b4d2a7b00144d954afb903ba7","tid":2491778,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:41:28.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"8c1087dc90e26c0c84f72a044ebbf016c9c4aa32","tid":2491778,"uid":371112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:47:36.000Z","msg":"正字：主權移交<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> not 回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c1b069d5680147603e59404ca51b7544e5f927","tid":2491778,"uid":18063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaueBvnoKdjCcRNwhNgECwMFFzgJH1ygpANJaMAfoHkLg?filename=gXqxhiu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXqxhiu.jpg&h=c269e78f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢三隻杯推測係ESPRESSO，因為非常細隻<br />\n而因為係DUNN BENNETT製造嘅英國杯，是相當稀有的<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVVJpSrPJwa58DBKzTRR6kJtPBujUhNNNMQ6hbx2TvLh8?filename=WukmaD3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWukmaD3.jpg&h=c43a60f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖中）是一隻蛋杯<br />\n（圖右）推測是糖鹽罌<br />\n而（圖左），有說是糖鹽罌，也有說是另一種蛋杯<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWP4cs5GgwgPHDhYKcCxd9QyoCF1NiKoA9f1RM4oWxtkG?filename=OV8ZGMp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOV8ZGMp.jpg&h=9c23b330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除左上面常常提到嘅三個廠商<br />\n亦有一啲瓷器係特別嘅廠商製造<br />\n（圖左）是日本製的MOMOYAMA<br />\n（圖右）的瓷底寫著FUNCHBRO CHINA<br />\n我個人推測是在OCCUPIED JAPAN時期的日本製杯，並非中國製<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmch8fFrmog1cPtjS6G6oedvx66rJrTArAoDJ6RX3uY5bh?filename=ainDcT0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FainDcT0.jpg&h=fa5b233e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢種杯碟都比較常見，但不知道應否納入綠邊白瓷<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX9WkYVCkQerjLChZoHXemFdCuw241rh7aA5n72EdwmQn?filename=ckp9302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fckp9302.jpg&h=51482253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY5kSdd3Tf8JfMjSDmfFPmQD37T8ei372Mzch1zwv1Q7t?filename=KE6kren.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKE6kren.jpg&h=5255fb23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剛剛所說，已知最早的廠商是英國的DUNN BENNETT<br />\n但比DUNN BENNETT更早的會是什麼廠商，仍是一個謎<br />\n上圖中的橢圓碟和圓形碗，左邊的是MATSUMURA出產<br />\n而右邊的，雖然有點像TOYO，都是灰灰的，但又不完全一樣<br />\nTOYO出產的瓷器成品穩定，較少變數<br />\n而據聞右邊的碗碟，正是比DUNN BENNETT更早的瓷器<br />\n但沒有證據<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNV2kUxswdkmVtg6mJCk29V8WN68KYTYTngqBqqjGV13g?filename=tFZ2EA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFZ2EA8.jpg&h=fa0d1528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了綠邊白瓷，政府餐具還有膠造的<br />\n而我只有很少膠造餐具<br />\n除了圖中的盤碟外，還有膠碗、膠羹、膠汁壺、膠蛋杯<br />\n都是很稀有的<br />\n<br />\n我的分享就到此為止啦<br />\n都市傳說中其實仲有很多只聽其名，未見其物嘅綠邊白瓷<br />\n例如瓷羹、超大的無蓋水壺、方形碟等等<br />\n如果有人可以分享一下就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外提提大家，市面上也有一些新造的重製品，也有一些膺品<br />\n其實個設計咁靚，傳承落去都係好事<br />\n只係如果想作為文物收藏，就要小心啦"},{"pid":"0e3d113e56e5e5612c752b01bc442c7cc10909d3","tid":2491778,"uid":91317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"好靚，有冇廠可以整返，一定大賣"}]}